1
00:00:10,960 --> 00:00:13,420
♪The maple mark on your skin♪

2
00:00:14,230 --> 00:00:17,040
♪The only proof we exist♪

3
00:00:18,210 --> 00:00:21,450
♪I stole you back from destiny♪

4
00:00:21,560 --> 00:00:24,430
♪But can I redeem myself♪

5
00:00:24,430 --> 00:00:26,540
♪I don't care what fate foretells♪

6
00:00:26,750 --> 00:00:30,330
♪Or how rough the road may be♪

7
00:00:30,340 --> 00:00:33,280
♪Stay, I'll fight for you♪

8
00:00:33,610 --> 00:00:37,660
♪That's all I'll ever do♪

9
00:00:37,760 --> 00:00:39,890
♪If life is just a show♪

10
00:00:39,890 --> 00:00:42,650
♪I'll stay with you till the end♪

11
00:00:42,650 --> 00:00:44,980
♪I'm scared we'll wake up alone♪

12
00:00:44,980 --> 00:00:47,960
♪So don't let this dream end♪

13
00:00:47,960 --> 00:00:52,420
♪In my bones, in my heart♪

14
00:00:52,420 --> 00:00:54,100
♪I know I'll have to leave♪

15
00:00:54,100 --> 00:00:55,670
♪You must not leave my side♪

16
00:00:55,670 --> 00:00:57,260
♪No place can hold us in♪

17
00:00:57,260 --> 00:01:01,910
♪Not when it's you and me♪

18
00:01:06,890 --> 00:01:10,400
♪Forever♪

19
00:01:11,490 --> 00:01:15,250
♪In my soul♪

20
00:01:17,260 --> 00:01:23,300
=This Palace Maid Isn't Very Calm=
=Episode 8=

21
00:01:27,120 --> 00:01:28,640
Greetings, Your Highness.

22
00:01:28,920 --> 00:01:31,640
I'll never forget your kindness.

23
00:01:31,640 --> 00:01:33,120
I'll serve you well

24
00:01:33,200 --> 00:01:34,400
and wish you a long life.

25
00:01:34,400 --> 00:01:35,760
Rise.

26
00:01:36,690 --> 00:01:37,790
Thank you, Your Highness.

27
00:01:37,790 --> 00:01:38,950
Look at you.

28
00:01:38,950 --> 00:01:40,310
Still sweet-talking.

29
00:01:40,510 --> 00:01:42,760
Though I made you a physician,

30
00:01:43,150 --> 00:01:45,640
my kitchen still needs you.

31
00:01:46,430 --> 00:01:48,400
You'll handle

32
00:01:48,400 --> 00:01:50,070
my meals as before.

33
00:01:50,160 --> 00:01:51,000
Understood.

34
00:01:51,120 --> 00:01:53,160
What would you like for dinner?

35
00:01:53,190 --> 00:01:54,280
I'll prepare it immediately.

36
00:01:55,200 --> 00:01:57,070
I'm the patient here.

37
00:01:57,230 --> 00:01:58,950
What I eat

38
00:01:58,950 --> 00:02:00,590
is up to you.

39
00:02:02,950 --> 00:02:03,790
By the way,

40
00:02:04,310 --> 00:02:05,590
the new candidates

41
00:02:06,000 --> 00:02:08,000
will meet the Emperor soon.

42
00:02:08,240 --> 00:02:09,870
Prepare an extra dish

43
00:02:09,870 --> 00:02:11,470
for each of them

44
00:02:11,630 --> 00:02:13,310
from Cining Palace today.

45
00:02:13,870 --> 00:02:14,910
As you wish.

46
00:02:15,190 --> 00:02:16,280
Consider it done.

47
00:02:20,470 --> 00:02:22,000
(Main quest finally starts.)

48
00:02:22,000 --> 00:02:22,910
(Once I finish it,)

49
00:02:22,910 --> 00:02:24,560
(maybe I can go home.)

50
00:02:24,630 --> 00:02:26,590
(Zhi Hui took 10 years
to be Empress.)

51
00:02:26,590 --> 00:02:28,000
(With me, she might)

52
00:02:28,000 --> 00:02:29,030
(reach the top in one.)

53
00:02:29,480 --> 00:02:31,470
Distribute these dishes.

54
00:02:31,470 --> 00:02:34,190
Tell the ladies it's a reward

55
00:02:34,190 --> 00:02:35,280
from the Dowager's grace.

56
00:02:35,470 --> 00:02:36,310
Yes.

57
00:02:44,150 --> 00:02:45,680
Greetings, Miss Zhi Hui.

58
00:02:46,190 --> 00:02:47,960
Ye Jin, what brings you here?

59
00:02:48,190 --> 00:02:51,280
I work in the Dowager's
kitchen now.

60
00:02:51,400 --> 00:02:54,000
She sent a dish
for all the candidates,

61
00:02:54,000 --> 00:02:56,240
so I brought yours.

62
00:02:56,840 --> 00:02:58,590
Come on. Sit down.

63
00:03:00,240 --> 00:03:02,080
No need for formalities.

64
00:03:02,240 --> 00:03:04,360
Just call me Hui.

65
00:03:04,360 --> 00:03:05,200
Hui.

66
00:03:07,280 --> 00:03:08,240
What's this?

67
00:03:09,680 --> 00:03:12,030
I haven't been feeling well lately.

68
00:03:12,280 --> 00:03:14,590
Luckily, Yunxi went to the Imperial Clinic

69
00:03:14,590 --> 00:03:16,280
to get me a prescription

70
00:03:16,590 --> 00:03:18,030
for this calming tonic.

71
00:03:18,080 --> 00:03:19,470
I've been taking it for days,

72
00:03:19,590 --> 00:03:21,400
and I feel much better.

73
00:03:22,560 --> 00:03:23,400
Wait.

74
00:03:23,960 --> 00:03:25,630
This isn't right.

75
00:03:28,360 --> 00:03:30,030
After drinking it,

76
00:03:30,030 --> 00:03:31,800
do you feel cold
in your lower abdomen?

77
00:03:33,560 --> 00:03:35,590
Why? Anything wrong?

78
00:03:35,870 --> 00:03:38,280
I smell saffron.

79
00:03:39,190 --> 00:03:41,840
It's a powerful blood-thinner.

80
00:03:41,840 --> 00:03:43,630
Long-term use

81
00:03:43,630 --> 00:03:45,590
harms vitality and chills the womb.

82
00:03:45,590 --> 00:03:46,840
Over time,

83
00:03:46,960 --> 00:03:48,360
you'll be unable to bear children.

84
00:03:48,360 --> 00:03:49,520
What?

85
00:03:50,150 --> 00:03:51,000
But...

86
00:03:51,430 --> 00:03:54,080
the prescription was
from the Imperial Clinic.

87
00:03:54,190 --> 00:03:56,150
Maybe.

88
00:03:56,150 --> 00:03:59,030
But who says

89
00:03:59,430 --> 00:04:01,000
nothing was added

90
00:04:01,000 --> 00:04:02,870
on the way here?

91
00:04:04,560 --> 00:04:06,280
Who would harm me?

92
00:04:07,470 --> 00:04:09,360
If you can't bear a child,

93
00:04:09,750 --> 00:04:11,430
even favor

94
00:04:11,630 --> 00:04:14,150
won't save you.

95
00:04:14,630 --> 00:04:15,710
Who benefits

96
00:04:15,960 --> 00:04:17,040
from that?

97
00:04:18,600 --> 00:04:21,040
Everyone's a suspect.

98
00:04:21,750 --> 00:04:23,430
But there is only one

99
00:04:23,680 --> 00:04:25,750
whom I would trust enough

100
00:04:26,270 --> 00:04:27,480
to take it from.

101
00:04:28,560 --> 00:04:29,400
Yunxi.

102
00:04:31,630 --> 00:04:32,760
What do you plan to do?

103
00:04:33,870 --> 00:04:34,900
I don't know.

104
00:04:35,430 --> 00:04:36,850
My mind is a mess.

105
00:04:37,270 --> 00:04:38,770
I took her as a friend.

106
00:04:39,680 --> 00:04:41,040
I can't believe she…

107
00:04:41,040 --> 00:04:42,600
If you trust me,

108
00:04:42,870 --> 00:04:44,390
I have a plan.

109
00:04:48,430 --> 00:04:49,390
Help.

110
00:04:49,390 --> 00:04:50,360
Someone. Help.

111
00:04:50,360 --> 00:04:51,750
Miss Zhi Hui fainted.

112
00:04:51,750 --> 00:04:53,000
Call a physician.

113
00:04:53,360 --> 00:04:54,800
Inform Consort Lan.

114
00:04:54,800 --> 00:04:55,950
Tell her it's Chuxiu Palace.

115
00:04:55,950 --> 00:04:56,790
Yes.

116
00:05:13,160 --> 00:05:14,270
Hui.

117
00:05:14,270 --> 00:05:17,040
(Gua'erjia Yunxi)
Hui, wake up. Don't scare me.

118
00:05:24,160 --> 00:05:25,560
Greetings, Ladies.

119
00:05:25,950 --> 00:05:27,000
Miss Yunxi,

120
00:05:27,360 --> 00:05:29,510
I heard you've been

121
00:05:29,680 --> 00:05:31,360
caring for her

122
00:05:31,630 --> 00:05:33,120
and bringing her medicine every day.

123
00:05:34,630 --> 00:05:36,390
We are like sisters.

124
00:05:36,750 --> 00:05:37,600
It's only right

125
00:05:38,160 --> 00:05:39,480
that I care for her.

126
00:05:39,480 --> 00:05:42,600
Which physician wrote the prescription?

127
00:05:43,830 --> 00:05:44,670
It was

128
00:05:47,750 --> 00:05:49,240
Physician Zhang.

129
00:05:50,480 --> 00:05:51,360
Physician Zhang?

130
00:05:51,720 --> 00:05:52,560
Yes.

131
00:05:54,800 --> 00:05:55,830
Is this the prescription

132
00:05:55,830 --> 00:05:56,800
you wrote?

133
00:05:58,120 --> 00:05:58,960
Coptis,

134
00:05:59,200 --> 00:06:00,040
cypress seed,

135
00:06:00,040 --> 00:06:00,880
polygala,

136
00:06:01,070 --> 00:06:01,920
jujube seed...

137
00:06:02,040 --> 00:06:04,680
Yes, it's a calming formula.

138
00:06:05,040 --> 00:06:06,070
And this?

139
00:06:06,560 --> 00:06:08,190
Saffron, peach kernel,

140
00:06:08,190 --> 00:06:09,080
salvia...

141
00:06:09,090 --> 00:06:10,600
All blood-thinning herbs.

142
00:06:10,630 --> 00:06:13,190
Nothing calms the nerves.

143
00:06:32,000 --> 00:06:34,160
There is saffron in the tonic.

144
00:06:34,560 --> 00:06:36,000
Long-term use

145
00:06:36,040 --> 00:06:38,160
leads to depletion of vitality

146
00:06:38,240 --> 00:06:40,160
or even infertility.

147
00:06:40,190 --> 00:06:42,240
This is not my prescription.

148
00:06:43,630 --> 00:06:44,720
Miss Yunxi,

149
00:06:44,720 --> 00:06:46,560
you brought her the tonic daily.

150
00:06:46,560 --> 00:06:47,800
Now that it has come to this,

151
00:06:48,000 --> 00:06:50,040
care to explain?

152
00:07:00,830 --> 00:07:02,190
You lowly maid.

153
00:07:02,560 --> 00:07:04,870
How dare you accuse me?

154
00:07:06,270 --> 00:07:07,950
What about me?

155
00:07:07,950 --> 00:07:12,070
Am I qualified?

156
00:07:14,560 --> 00:07:18,160
I know the rivalries

157
00:07:18,160 --> 00:07:19,600
among the candidates,

158
00:07:20,270 --> 00:07:23,600
but I didn't think someone would

159
00:07:23,600 --> 00:07:25,630
dare to tamper with medicine.

160
00:07:25,870 --> 00:07:27,390
If I don't investigate,

161
00:07:27,390 --> 00:07:28,950
how do I answer to the Emperor

162
00:07:28,950 --> 00:07:30,630
and the Dowager?

163
00:07:31,920 --> 00:07:33,190
Your Highness.

164
00:07:33,190 --> 00:07:34,360
I'm innocent.

165
00:07:34,360 --> 00:07:35,480
I had no idea.

166
00:07:35,480 --> 00:07:36,870
Your Highness.

167
00:07:36,870 --> 00:07:38,190
We'll see

168
00:07:38,190 --> 00:07:39,430
about that.

169
00:07:40,270 --> 00:07:41,240
Guards.

170
00:07:41,560 --> 00:07:42,750
Take her

171
00:07:43,120 --> 00:07:44,240
for investigation.

172
00:07:44,750 --> 00:07:46,390
No. Your Highness.

173
00:07:46,390 --> 00:07:47,870
I had no idea.

174
00:07:47,870 --> 00:07:48,800
Your Highness.

175
00:07:54,750 --> 00:07:55,590
Hui.

176
00:07:55,630 --> 00:07:57,560
Get up. They're gone.

177
00:08:05,630 --> 00:08:06,920
Was that

178
00:08:06,920 --> 00:08:08,480
too much?

179
00:08:08,710 --> 00:08:09,560
Yunxi...

180
00:08:09,560 --> 00:08:10,400
What?

181
00:08:10,950 --> 00:08:11,920
Are you getting soft?

182
00:08:15,480 --> 00:08:17,040
If she succeeded,

183
00:08:17,480 --> 00:08:18,950
I'd be infertile for life.

184
00:08:19,600 --> 00:08:20,600
Then,

185
00:08:21,120 --> 00:08:22,630
who would pity me?

186
00:08:22,680 --> 00:08:24,830
I'm glad you understand.

187
00:08:25,270 --> 00:08:28,240
Three days till audience.

188
00:08:28,430 --> 00:08:30,270
No time for emotions.

189
00:08:30,270 --> 00:08:31,480
Pull yourself together.

190
00:08:31,480 --> 00:08:34,200
Think about how to stand out.

191
00:08:34,870 --> 00:08:37,670
It's all about his favor.

192
00:08:38,080 --> 00:08:39,840
I'm nothing special.

193
00:08:40,080 --> 00:08:41,670
How can I stand out?

194
00:08:41,840 --> 00:08:42,680
Come on.

195
00:08:42,960 --> 00:08:44,480
Don't belittle yourself.

196
00:08:44,870 --> 00:08:46,080
To me,

197
00:08:46,080 --> 00:08:49,270
only four standouts this year.

198
00:08:49,440 --> 00:08:50,750
Yunxi is charming.

199
00:08:50,960 --> 00:08:52,150
Xiao Rou is a beauty.

200
00:08:52,360 --> 00:08:53,630
Liu Mei is vibrant.

201
00:08:54,030 --> 00:08:55,600
You are gentle and elegant.

202
00:08:57,200 --> 00:08:58,240
Now,

203
00:08:58,240 --> 00:08:59,960
Yunxi's out.

204
00:09:00,030 --> 00:09:02,270
Two rivals left.

205
00:09:03,870 --> 00:09:05,080
We need a plan

206
00:09:05,080 --> 00:09:08,030
to remove them before the audience

207
00:09:08,750 --> 00:09:11,240
so you can shine.

208
00:09:11,600 --> 00:09:12,670
Remove?

209
00:09:12,840 --> 00:09:13,680
Exactly.

210
00:09:14,720 --> 00:09:15,910
Remove them.

211
00:09:33,670 --> 00:09:34,510
Your Highness.

212
00:09:34,870 --> 00:09:36,550
His Majesty reached the gate,

213
00:09:36,600 --> 00:09:38,750
but Consort Duan's servant

214
00:09:39,150 --> 00:09:41,200
said she fell ill.

215
00:09:41,200 --> 00:09:43,870
He went to her instead.

216
00:09:46,360 --> 00:09:47,320
That woman again.

217
00:09:48,270 --> 00:09:51,080
She keeps stealing him away from me.

218
00:09:51,600 --> 00:09:53,360
Does she think I'm powerless?

219
00:09:53,870 --> 00:09:55,150
Calm down, Your Highness.

220
00:09:55,150 --> 00:09:56,270
Calm down?

221
00:09:57,270 --> 00:09:59,600
How can I?

222
00:09:59,870 --> 00:10:01,360
Perhaps

223
00:10:01,440 --> 00:10:03,670
you should pick a few talented girls

224
00:10:03,670 --> 00:10:05,320
from the new candidates

225
00:10:05,550 --> 00:10:07,080
and send them to His Majesty.

226
00:10:07,360 --> 00:10:08,790
Once he has someone new,

227
00:10:08,840 --> 00:10:11,240
Consort Duan won't be able
to use her pregnancy to…

228
00:10:11,240 --> 00:10:12,080
Shut up.

229
00:10:12,750 --> 00:10:15,080
Her Highness is devoted to His Majesty.

230
00:10:15,150 --> 00:10:16,720
Sending him more women

231
00:10:16,720 --> 00:10:18,360
will only distress her.

232
00:10:20,480 --> 00:10:21,600
I'm sorry.

233
00:10:21,600 --> 00:10:22,630
I deserve punishment.

234
00:10:22,750 --> 00:10:23,910
I'm sorry.

235
00:10:24,120 --> 00:10:25,150
I deserve punishment.

236
00:10:26,510 --> 00:10:27,360
Your Highness.

237
00:10:27,360 --> 00:10:29,240
Physician Ye Jin requests audience.

238
00:10:29,240 --> 00:10:30,390
Perfect timing.

239
00:10:30,840 --> 00:10:31,840
Let her in.

240
00:10:36,600 --> 00:10:38,360
Greetings, Your Highness.

241
00:10:38,980 --> 00:10:39,820
Rise.

242
00:10:39,820 --> 00:10:40,960
Thank you.

243
00:10:41,440 --> 00:10:44,090
I heard you spent days in the labor camp

244
00:10:44,200 --> 00:10:46,510
and then won the Dowager's favor
with a medical manual.

245
00:10:47,070 --> 00:10:49,480
You were even appointed as a physician.

246
00:10:49,480 --> 00:10:51,360
You've got quite the bag of tricks.

247
00:10:52,120 --> 00:10:53,670
Why are you

248
00:10:53,670 --> 00:10:55,030
here today?

249
00:10:55,360 --> 00:10:56,670
I'm here

250
00:10:56,670 --> 00:10:58,630
to ease your worries.

251
00:10:59,030 --> 00:11:01,910
A physician

252
00:11:02,120 --> 00:11:03,510
easing worries?

253
00:11:03,510 --> 00:11:05,720
I can ease your worries

254
00:11:05,720 --> 00:11:07,320
and fix your problems.

255
00:11:07,510 --> 00:11:09,440
Rumors say

256
00:11:09,510 --> 00:11:12,360
Consort Duan keeps His Majesty

257
00:11:12,360 --> 00:11:14,390
from visiting you.

258
00:11:15,150 --> 00:11:16,720
You must feel

259
00:11:16,840 --> 00:11:20,480
chest tightness,

260
00:11:20,870 --> 00:11:22,270
poor appetite,

261
00:11:22,440 --> 00:11:23,600
and insomnia.

262
00:11:25,360 --> 00:11:26,870
I have a solution

263
00:11:26,870 --> 00:11:29,240
to cure that.

264
00:11:29,960 --> 00:11:31,360
Go on.

265
00:11:31,630 --> 00:11:33,080
Tell me about it.

266
00:11:33,080 --> 00:11:35,510
You should make use

267
00:11:35,550 --> 00:11:38,080
of the new candidates.

268
00:11:38,720 --> 00:11:41,320
You want me to share favor too?

269
00:11:42,840 --> 00:11:44,120
Of course not.

270
00:11:44,320 --> 00:11:47,240
You need authority.

271
00:11:47,240 --> 00:11:48,720
Not favor.

272
00:11:49,150 --> 00:11:51,080
Everyone knows her authority

273
00:11:51,080 --> 00:11:52,510
in the palace.

274
00:11:53,030 --> 00:11:54,670
With your noble rank

275
00:11:54,670 --> 00:11:56,440
and power of life and death,

276
00:11:56,440 --> 00:11:57,910
everyone fears you.

277
00:11:58,120 --> 00:12:01,270
But they fear your power,

278
00:12:01,360 --> 00:12:03,670
not you.

279
00:12:04,510 --> 00:12:06,720
Consort Duan is pregnant.

280
00:12:06,720 --> 00:12:07,960
Her worth is rising

281
00:12:07,960 --> 00:12:10,150
with her unborn child.

282
00:12:10,150 --> 00:12:12,720
Everyone here is an opportunist.

283
00:12:13,000 --> 00:12:14,910
Unless you secure

284
00:12:14,910 --> 00:12:16,510
your prestige now,

285
00:12:16,840 --> 00:12:20,030
your reign over the harem will

286
00:12:20,720 --> 00:12:23,150
be in jeopardy

287
00:12:23,150 --> 00:12:24,510
the moment her son is born.

288
00:12:24,750 --> 00:12:25,590
How dare you?

289
00:12:37,870 --> 00:12:39,440
Then tell me,

290
00:12:41,750 --> 00:12:43,960
what should I do?

291
00:12:44,510 --> 00:12:46,240
Gain their loyalty, of course.

292
00:12:46,320 --> 00:12:47,160
The new girls

293
00:12:47,190 --> 00:12:48,150
have no allegiances yet.

294
00:12:48,720 --> 00:12:50,440
It's the best time to control them.

295
00:12:50,550 --> 00:12:53,150
Host a banquet

296
00:12:53,480 --> 00:12:54,910
and invite them all.

297
00:12:55,030 --> 00:12:56,240
Show them

298
